Migrate KUTTL resources to Chainsaw

Usage:
  chainsaw migrate [flags]
  chainsaw migrate [command]

Available Commands:
  config      Migrate KUTTL config to Chainsaw
  tests       Migrate KUTTL tests to Chainsaw

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for migrate

Use "chainsaw migrate [command] --help" for more information about a command.
